    <p>Takeaway</p>
    <p>Leaked (shared) information should NOT be linkable unless REALLY necessary</p>
    <p>Linkability: a useful but MISSING notion in the mobile ecosystem</p>
    <p>Anonymous (unlinkable) in-app behaviors should be a BASIC right</p>
